# Kuberns Configuration

This repository is connected to Kuberns for automated deployments.

The Kuberns agent monitors this repository and triggers deployment pipelines on every push to the configured branch.

## How it works

- On every push, the Kuberns agent picks up the latest commit and begins the build process.
- The agent provisions the required infrastructure, builds your application, and deploys it to the target environment.
- Deployment logs and status updates are available in real time on your Kuberns dashboard.

